er satellite, and furthermore suggest that combining\nensemble methods for spots and flares could overcome the limitations of each\nindividual technique for the localization of surface magnetic fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 3 Jun 2023 05:38:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-06"}
